Class CoinDispenserBronze

java.lang.Object
com.tdc.AbstractComponent<CoinDispenserObserver>
com.tdc.coin.AbstractCoinDispenser
com.tdc.coin.CoinDispenserBronze
All Implemented Interfaces:
ICoinDispenser, IComponent<CoinDispenserObserver>, Source<Coin>
public final class CoinDispenserBronze extends AbstractCoinDispenser
Represents a component that stores coins of a particular denomination to dispense them as change. This component cannot be automatically refilled from its source.
Author:
TDC, Inc.
